Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:23.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}夕方の風はやさしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:31.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}並んで君と歩いた今日が
