Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:17.40,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}似是要吹凉发烫的脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:23.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}傍晚的风是如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:31.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}与你并肩漫步的今日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:35.25,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}便成了一生难忘的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:38.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}你不经意间的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:41.80,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}我心里再清楚不过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:47.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}但思绪就是静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:51.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}只是一句话就让我脸红心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:54.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}心中萌生小小情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:23:01.86,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}仿佛让我置身梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.95,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}内心为何如此欣喜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:09.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}可又为何如此悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}此刻 我依然在你身边眺望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:16.71,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}将你的侧颜深深刻进脑海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:23.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}你我之间如此相近的距离
